<h2>About Us</h2>
@*<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>*@

<div id="aboutUs"class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"; style="text-align:center">
<p>
    SafeKeepers QR is designed to offer parents and guardians a sense of security knowing first responders
    have quick and easy access to all important and lifesaving information related to their child.
</p>

<p>3 Simple Steps</p>

<p>Create your child's online profile containing a photo, medical information, emergency contacts and more.
    All information included in the profile will be public for use in case of an emergency.</p>

    <p>Print your child's customized QR code on stickers, temporary tattoos, clothing or other materials of your choice.</p>

    <p>Scan the QR code using a mobile phone or tablet for a quick look at your child's profile.</p>
</div>